data.description:
This large home is partially renovated and ready for someone to turn it into their dream home.  The home could easily have a separate living suite by for a mother/father or adult child.  The master bedroom suite is massive or could be used as two bedrooms.

The three car garage, dual zoned hvac, large utility room, hobby room and pool area add to the potential of this home.   Chandelier in dining room and breakfast nook do not transfer.
